OL,3,CNew venue hosting Aston Villa fan park
OL,4,Cafter stabbing forces move
OL,6,FA new venue has been found for Aston
OL,7,FVilla fans hoping to watch the UEFA
OL,8,FEuropa League Final in Birmingham next
OL,9,Fweek after a double stabbing meant the
OL,10,Fprevious venue lost its licence.
OL,12,FThe Aston Villa UEFA Europa League
OL,13,FFinal fan park was due to be held at
OL,14,FLuna Springs, but the Digbeth
OL,15,Fnightclub has had its licence
OL,16,Fsuspended for 28 days after an attack
OL,17,Flast weekend.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
