OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778875555
OL,3,CNew venue hosting Aston Villa fan park
OL,4,Cafter stabbing forces move
OL,6,FIt means fan park organisers,
OL,7,F4TheFans, have been searching for a
OL,8,Fnew venue for the event on Wednesday,
OL,9,FMay 20, which had already sold dozens
OL,10,Fof tickets.
OL,12,FThe event will be moved to the city's
OL,13,FUtilita Arena in what 4TheFans called
OL,14,Fthe "biggest-ever fan park experience".
OL,16,FThe move will give thousands of Villa
OL,17,Ffans the chance to watch the Europa
OL,18,FLeague final on anti-glare screens
OL,19,Fwith world-class sound systems.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
