FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778875555
OL,3,CNew venue hosting Aston Villa fan park
OL,4,Cafter stabbing forces move
OL,6,FTwo unconfirmed Aston Villa football
OL,7,Flegends will also provide analysis
OL,8,Fthroughout the game. There will also
OL,9,Fbe DJs and entertainment, special
OL,10,Feffects and a fully stocked bar.
OL,12,FDoors will open at 5 pm, ahead of the
OL,13,F8 pm kick-off.
OL,15,FA spokesman for 4TheFans said:
OL,16,F"4TheFans worked quickly to secure one
OL,17,Fof the UK's biggest indoor arenas -
OL,18,Fthere are no limits to how big this
OL,19,Ffan park can get.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
