PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778875555
OL,3,CNew venue hosting Aston Villa fan park
OL,4,Cafter stabbing forces move
OL,6,F"With the unstoppable claret and blue
OL,7,Farmy coming together to mark this
OL,8,Fhistoric moment, the 4TheFans fan park
OL,9,Fwill deliver a genuine, stadium-like
OL,10,Fatmosphere as fans roar Villa towards
OL,11,Fthe club's first European trophy since
OL,12,F1982.
OL,14,F"One thing is guaranteed at Utilita -
OL,15,Fthe claret-and-blue support will be
OL,16,Fevery bit as noisy, passionate, and
OL,17,Ffierce as anything inside Besiktas
OL,18,FPark.
