PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778875555
OL,3,CNew venue hosting Aston Villa fan park
OL,4,Cafter stabbing forces move
OL,6,F"Utilita Arena has hosted the
OL,7,FCommonwealth Games, the World Indoor
OL,8,FChampionships, Elton John, WWE, The
OL,9,FEurovision Song Contest, Les
OL,10,FMiserables - the list of huge, world-
OL,11,Ffamous events goes on. Now 4theFans is
OL,12,Fjoining with Villa fans to create
OL,13,Fanother historic event.
OL,15,F"Whatever happens, ecstasy or
OL,16,Fheartbreak, this is a match that Villa
OL,17,Ffans need to experience together, and
OL,18,Fit doesn't get any bigger or better
OL,19,Fthan 4TheFans at Utilita Arena."
OL,26,@rD@Drr
